&lt;h1 id=&#34;intro-to-monster-design-for-2-d-games&#34;&gt;Intro to monster design for 2-D games&lt;/h1&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The intro to monster design is the first free training released on GDquest. In about 40 minutes, it will &lt;strong&gt;run you through the thought process a game artist might follow to design monsters&lt;/strong&gt;. It both covers the thought process behind the design of a monster and an example of monster drawing with pen, paper and Krita.&lt;/p&gt;

